-- IFC Increases Trade Credit Line to EFG Eurobank to $50 Million
-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 2012-04-24T10:22:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/ifc-increases-trade-credit-line-to-efg-eurobank-to-50-million.html
The International Finance Corp.,
the World Bank’s investment unit, said it will increase a trade
credit line to  EFG Eurobank Ergasias SA (EUROB) ’s Romanian unit to $50
million to help local importers and exporters enter new markets,
the Washington-based lender said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
